# Axiom v2 — Full Implementation Plan (Phases 1–9)

> **Scope**: 9 phases, all on-device, extending the existing Expo + Supabase + Zustand architecture.
> **Principle**: Extend, don't rewrite. Every phase builds on existing services.
> **Estimated Total**: ~24–30 dev days across 9 iterations.

